{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T12:33:54.893551Z", "created_at": "Wed Feb 15 20:20:16 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-02-15T20:20:16Z", "created_at_ts": 1676492416, "display_name": "Elissa Slotkin", "handle": "elissaslotkin", "id": "1625953160362659868", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 599, \"reply_count\": 179, \"like_count\": 5880, \"quote_count\": 53, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "This is how I know the ground is shifting in Michigan on the issue of gun safety: Since Monday, I’ve received more messages of support for MSU than I can count, including a ton of texts &amp; calls from Republican constituents &amp; leaders who I know to be avid hunters &amp; sportsmen. 1/", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "ElissaSlotkin"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T12:33:54.893551Z", "created_at": "Wed Feb 15 20:20:17 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-02-15T20:20:17Z", "created_at_ts": 1676492417, "display_name": "Elissa Slotkin", "handle": "elissaslotkin", "id": "1625953162187182109", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 90, \"reply_count\": 4, \"like_count\": 1175, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "2/ These folks call to tell me that while they love their hobby &amp; don’t want someone taking their guns, they also can’t stand to see the gun violence we’re seeing again and again and again. These folks are just as fed up and angry as anyone who’s been calling me.", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "ElissaSlotkin"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T12:33:54.893551Z", "created_at": "Wed Feb 15 20:20:17 +0000 2023", "created_at_iso": "2023-02-15T20:20:17Z", "created_at_ts": 1676492417, "display_name": "Elissa Slotkin", "handle": "elissaslotkin", "id": "1625953164485660687", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 76, \"reply_count\": 1, \"like_count\": 1016, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "3/ They are parents and grandparents who are watching our children change because of gun violence, and they want something done. I started to see this after Oxford, it deepened with Uvalde, and now it’s ramped up even more after the shooting at MSU.", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "ElissaSlotkin"}
